## Summary

| Severity | Count | Top Issue |
|----------|-------|-----------|
| 🔴 Critical | 4 | `Underscore()` triple-regex chain: 4 allocations/call × millions of calls |
| 🟡 Moderate | 3 | `UnderscoreRegex` not using `[GeneratedRegex]`; `InflectionRule` compiled-per-instance + double execution |
| ℹ️ Info | 1 | Unsealed `InflectionRule` class |

